---
---
<header class="relative pt-20 pb-24 md:pt-28 md:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="fade-in inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full glass text-xs muted mb-7 border-white/10">
      <span class="inline-block size-1.5 rounded-full bg-mint-500 animate-pulse"></span>
      <span class="font-mono">v1.0 spec · CC0 public domain · MIT parsers</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-[0.95] max-w-4xl">
      <span class="gradient-text">ASHRU</span><br/>
      <span class="text-ink-100">Atomic Semantic</span><br/>
      <span class="text-ink-100">Hyper-Relational Unit.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 text-xl md:text-2xl text-ink-100 leading-snug mt-7 max-w-3xl font-medium">
      The deterministic semantic transport protocol for AI. <span class="gradient-text">JSON was designed for humans writing APIs. ASHRU is designed for machines generating semantics.</span>
    </p>

    <p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 text-lg muted leading-relaxed mt-6 max-w-2xl">
      <strong class="text-ink-100">Coming from JSON?</strong> ASHRU drops 60–80% of your output tokens by killing
      the brackets, quotes, and repeated field names. <strong class="text-ink-100">Coming from TOON?</strong>
      ASHRU keeps the pipe compression and adds the six grammatical slots TOON leaves on the table —
      so retrieval is structural, not just compressed.
    </p>

    <p class="fade-in fade-in-delay-2 text-base muted mt-3 max-w-2xl">
      Built on the case roles Pāṇini formalized in Sanskrit 2,500 years ago, and the AI-knowledge-representation
      thesis Rick Briggs published at NASA in 1985. Public domain. Drop-in compatible with every LLM you already use.
    </p>

    <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-3 flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-10">
      <a href="#converter"
         class="px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white font-semibold transition-colors text-sm">
        Try the live converter →
      </a>
      <a href="#math"
         class="px-5 py-3 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 text-ink-100 font-semibold transition-colors text-sm">
        See the math
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/ashru-format/ashru-format"
         class="px-5 py-3 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 text-ink-300 font-semibold transition-colors text-sm">
        GitHub →
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero side-by-side -->
    <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-4 mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 md:p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs muted mb-4">
          <span class="font-mono">JSON output · ~120 tokens</span>
          <span class="text-flame-300 font-mono">$0.000048/record</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="code-block !bg-transparent !border-0 !p-0 text-[0.78rem] leading-relaxed"><code>{`{`}
  "verbs": [{`{`}
    "verb_lemma": "buy",
    "kartā": "Suman",
    "karma": "Tesla",
    "karaṇa": "$60000",
    "apādāna": "John",
    "adhikaraṇa": "SF",
    "tense": "past",
    "is_negated": false
  {`}`}]
{`}`}</code></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-5 md:p-6 glass" style="border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.25); background: rgba(139,92,246,0.04);">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs muted mb-4">
          <span class="font-mono">ASHRU output · ~25 tokens</span>
          <span class="text-mint-400 font-mono">$0.000010/record</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="code-block !bg-transparent !border-0 !p-0 text-[0.78rem] leading-relaxed"><code>ASHRU/1
V|buy|Suman|Tesla|$60000||John|SF|p|0|</code></pre>
        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
          <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold gradient-text">79.2% smaller</div>
          <div class="text-xs muted mt-1">Output side. Same fact. Math below.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats strip -->
    <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-4 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mt-10">
      <div class="glass rounded-xl px-4 py-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold">4.8×</div>
        <div class="text-xs muted mt-1">smaller per record</div>
      </div>
      <div class="glass rounded-xl px-4 py-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold">~80%</div>
        <div class="text-xs muted mt-1">output token savings</div>
      </div>
      <div class="glass rounded-xl px-4 py-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold">0</div>
        <div class="text-xs muted mt-1">runtime dependencies</div>
      </div>
      <div class="glass rounded-xl px-4 py-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl font-extrabold">2,500</div>
        <div class="text-xs muted mt-1">years old (Pāṇini)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
